{"id": 3079, "genre": 1000, "title": "购物这件事都给你带来的哪些意料之外的\"小确焦虑\"？", "description": "买买买或许可以缓解焦虑，但似乎也会带来一些新的烦恼。（题图来自：iStock ©️ invincible_bulldog）", "record_count": 3195, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191204004700Ng9K53LZVDPvc0Wy.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-03T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6087, "title": "购物这件事都给你带来的哪些意料之外的\"小确焦虑\"？", "content": "购物这件事都给你带来的哪些意料之外的小确焦虑？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349991, "content": "搞不清到底是“商家/别人说你需要”，还是自己真的需要", "image": "img/option/option/20191203233540XWGQ9CavHoStlTsP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349992, "content": "过于丰富的商品种类和复杂的优惠规则带来的决策疲劳", "image": "img/option/option/20191203234054hIlq1aYV0BHFKtCi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349993, "content": "对没买到的东西有“错失恐惧”心理（买到了又很容易失望", "image": "img/option/option/201912032345425R4Hxe63yfjlBGTQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349995, "content": "囤积太多物品之后带来的习惯性松鼠症和断舍离困难症", "image": "img/option/option/20191203235607qmaDZvIwuE0JRkMf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349996, "content": "拆完快递产生大量垃圾，带来“不环保”的微妙负罪感", "image": "img/option/option/20191203235549BNzIPnvp5mqh1wyH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349998, "content": "拥有新东西的快乐消失得越来越快，进入一种空虚循环", "image": "img/option/option/20191204001326hDRyPIZxoE3pwY1m.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349999, "content": "还信用卡的时候，总会陷入每月一次的“吃土恐惧”当中", "image": "img/option/option/20191204001836HehK65lIrQ3vasd0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350001, "content": "“通过消费让自己跟上时代”而产生的小型攀比和力不从心", "image": "img/option/option/20191204002732HEyP9hJWCorU53Fk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 350002, "content": "还好，我几乎没有这种感觉/我有其他类型的购物焦虑", "image": "img/option/option/20191204003243m5WMBiPcsgOfS03G.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}